parameters: The first place where Kru and I went on an adventure...
We sat around a campfire here and talked...
Back then, Kru seemed so lonely, he had a scent similar to mine...

His eyes looked as if he had given up on something, as if he was burdened
with deep thoughts...

Back then, I never imagined that I would go on such adventures with Kru,
that we would share so many laughs...
And that we would end up together...
But... I don't have the right... to feel this way...

The last time I saw Kru, he looked even smaller, weaker, and lonelier than
when we were talking here together...
In front of such a figure... what I did...
I was the one who cornered Kru...
There's no way I can be forgiven...
??? "There's no such thing as an unforgivable sin..."

??? "Every sin has a punishment... Once you've been punished, there's
nothing unforgivable..."
??? "What's important is the willingness to atone for your sins."

??? "Even if no one else understands... I do. I know that Umi has been
suffering all this time. That Umi has been fighting all along..."
How can I ever atone for it...
I don't care what becomes of me...
I want to save Kru... and everyone in the village...
If that can be my atonement...
I don't mind if I'm never forgiven...
アイキャッチ5タイトル
